# subscript(_:)

**Instance Subscript**

Accesses a contiguous range of elements with an unbounded range.

## Declaration

```swift
subscript(range: (UnboundedRange_) -> ()) -> DiscontiguousColumnSlice<WrappedElement> { get set }
```

## Parameters

- **range**: An unbounded range of valid indices in the column slice.

## Accessing Elements

- **subscript(_:)**: Accesses an element at an index.
- **subscript(_:)**: Accesses a contiguous range of elements.
- **subscript(_:)**: Accesses a contiguous range of elements with a range expression.
